                    be more strict on answer vagueness:

                Q1 Answer Completeness
                    - Do not make steps too vague like check the switch or run 
                    wires to the electrical box or install the GFCI. These need 
                    more steps or detail.", 
                    - Do not make assumptions like a drywall hole being small 
                    enough to use just compound.",

